room_title: Escape room "Knight's Quest" by Project: Escape in Atlanta
room_address: 1395 South Marietta Pkwy SE #202, Marietta, GA 30067
room_description: Inside of an aging castle, a secret room has recently been discovered. Rumors have been spreading that the room has been hiding several controversial relics. In order to protect these secrets, the government has decided to demolish the entire castle. How can you and your group of treasure hunters possibly resist? You'll have 60 minutes to recover the relics and escape the castle before the entire structure comes down on top of you.
